  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Organisation and logistic about realisation of vascular doppler ultrasound is something very
      eclectic . Need to shift patient from their bed , long waiting time and the effect on the
      hospital cost.

      That's why vascular yard aim to practise these doppler ultrasound directly in the patients'
      room in the bed.

      And like that evaluate the patient's satisfaction of this kind of coverage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
